==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mohr
<hw>Mohr</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A West
African gazelle (<spn>Gazella mohr</spn>), having horns on which are
eleven or twelve very prominent rings. It is one of the species which
produce bezoar.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>mhorr</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mohur</ent>⟦br⟧
